<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>Galdawt ing ie!</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Nuoi simlei ka len lai hin,
 Zinmang dogal sielang a lien;
 Ka ngai ie, henkawl nang bang ei sutpa,
 Ka kulhpi leh ka bitna pen, Ei nungsawn lo zen uo;

[V2]
 Galdawt ing ie Lalpa,
 Lungngaihna meipi zing mahleh;
 Ka lautha chawlhna ding Zion,
 Leh Na sakmel hawih chu.

[V3]
 2. Pak thing bangin hung lun zelin,
 Setan sausuon thim bang zingah;
 Khawvel ninnuom chena muong dente hi,
 Na lungsietna thun phawng dingin,
 Nungsul hawi lo dingin.

[V4]
 3. Maa I lawpnau leh nawpna,
 I Lalpau mel deihum tuoi nung;
 Tuhin lo bangin chul tadih mahleh,
 Nunnuom a I lenna dingun,
 Pakthing bang lun kit ding.

[V5]
 4. Gel zing hitiu, Zion vangkhuo,
 Lungdeih len-guol peh bang kimna;
 Lungtuokte luonthi nula khensa te'n,
 Sun nitin hai bang ei ngak ui,
 Kumsawt ninnawp lasa'n.</lyrics>
<hymn_number>111</hymn_number>
</song>